Chopped Canada - Season 1, Episode 11




The Sweet Taste of Success

This candy filled episode pits Quebec chefs vs. Ontario chefs in a heated battle for Chopped Canada Champion. Black licorice and candy coated chocolates cause sweet struggles in the first two rounds, while a basket of woodsy and spicy flavours turns things upside down when it comes time for dessert.




Original Air Date: 13-Mar-2014
